Package org.endeavourhealth.informationmanager.common Description

Provides the classes for he Discovery OWL ontology syntax and transforms to and from OWL2 functional syntax and the generation of snomed extensions for named classes

There are 3 main types of classes

Classes that model the Disovery syntax as JSON serializable classes

Classes that convert from Discovery to OWL2 (FS) and vice versa

Classes that apply Snomed IDs to hand generated IRIs, assuming the ontology has a Snomed ID counter

Since:
1.0
